README -- GEOS-Chem Unit Tester: perl/ subdirectory 
14 Apr 2015
GEOS-Chem Support Team
geos-chem-support@as.harvard.edu


Perl Modules:
-------------

Dates.pm       : Module w/ various date & time routines
UtUtils.pm     : Module w/ common routines for the GEOS-Chem Unit Tester


Perl Modules:
-------------
gcUnitTest     : Main driver script for the GEOS-Chem Unit Tester
gcCopyRunDirs  : Main driver script copying run directories from Unit Tester
cleanFiles     : Script to clean old files from logs & jobs subdirectories
validate       : Script to difference GEOS-Chem output files
getRunInfo     : Script to extract simulation information from input.geos


Input Files:
-------------
UnitTest.input   : Default input file for gcUnitTest.
CopyRunDir.input : Default input file for gcCopyRunDirs

NOTE: many other "template" versions of UnitTest.input (specifying different
options) may be found in the inputs/ subdirectory.

                 
Other Files:
-------------
Makefile         : Makefile used for Unit Tester run directories and run
                   directories copied from the Unit Tester
RunDirCopyREADME : Readme file for run directories copied from Unit Tester